<plot>In this show for kids, host Michael Young presented a weekly assortment of guests (including film and TV performers, well-known athletes, and consumer advocates with shopping tips for kids), musical performances and games. Each episode also included a segment called "Dear Alex and Annie", answering viewers' questions on a wide range of personal and social topics.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?291073</url></doc>
